org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator

Class NamedEntityNegationKernel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator.ConvolutionKernel
      • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.evaluator.NamedEntityNegationKernel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Kernel

    public class NamedEntityNegationKernel
extends ConvolutionKernel
    Evaluate negation status and certainty of named entities. If negation status differs, multiply convolution on concepts by -1. If certainty differs, multiply by 0.5. This assumes that possible values for certainty are certain/uncertain.
